			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Code still tbd, will change this description once done:\r\n- First, you need to meet Lakrissa (S_DEN_Tiefling_010_23129d6c-8d39-4a4c-a4f6-cfc6637b597c)  for the fist time at Elfsong,\r\n- Second, make a long rest.\r\n- Lakrissa will be on the rooftop making a short rest with Alfira\r\n- After speaking with both of them, Lakrissa will come back to the Taproom after other long rest."
				},
